The canonical agent guidance for this repo is in [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md). Read it for the
project overview, key file locations, commands, testing, code style, security, and hard
constraints. This rule is a thin adapter — do not duplicate policy here.

Key reminders:
- React + Vite SPA backed by Base44 (BaaS). Mobile-first (`max-w-lg mx-auto` on page roots).
- Never commit secrets or real Base44 credentials; keep `base44/.app.jsonc` a placeholder.
- `src/lib/matchData.js` is a static fixture list — do not fetch it dynamically.
- Wrap all new AI components in `<ErrorBoundary>`.
- Validate with `npm run agent:check && npm run lint && npm run typecheck && npm run test`.
